1982;;Far East;;Australian;;John Duigan;;Bryan Brown, Helen Morse, John Bell;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Far_East_(film);;Journalist Peter Reeves (John Bell) takes his wife Jo (Helen Morse) to the Far East. There they meet Morgan Keefe (Bryan Brown), an ex-pat Aussie who owns a sleazy bar/nightspot called "The Koala Klub". After renewing their romance, Jo seeks Morgan's help when her husband is persecuted by the military regime for his investigations.